    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "About this automation\n\nAn autonomous Market Intelligence & Content Generation Agent built specifically for digital marketing agencies. It tracks real-time industry shifts and converts raw news data into ready-to-publish social media strategies.\n\nHere's how it works:\n1. Schedule Trigger: Runs automatically at a set interval or triggers via the manual Start Button.\n2. Filter Logic: An \"IF\" flow control node manages execution timing and checks data prerequisites.\n3. HTTP Data Ingest: Connects to NewsAPI to fetch the latest top-performing articles matching specified trending business/AI keywords.\n4. Autonomous AI Agent: An advanced LLM processes the payload, coordinates with a Wikipedia tool for deeper brand/concept context, and drafts optimized LinkedIn/X hooks and an executive brief.\n5. Slack Delivery: Routes the finalized, fully formatted Markdown marketing assets directly to the agency's internal team communication hub.",
